Feature: Edit
    As a user
    I want to edit and view amount, date, category, description
    so that I know how much money I have

Scenario: Add to edit
    Given my expense balance have -100 baht
    When I add 100 to my expense
    Then I can view my expense balance is -200 baht

Scenario: Save edit
    Given my expense balance have -200 baht
    When I save edit my expense
    Then   my expense balance change to -200 baht
